dc_title_s: Ultoniae Orientalis; pars sumptibus Henrici Hondy.; Vltoniae Orientalis pars
dc_description_s: Relief shown pictorially. Does not match any states listed in Van der Krogt. From the Appendix Atlas of the British Isles and Northern Europe, title created to represent a unique collection within the Clark Library, University of Michigan. 1 map: 35 x 45 cm. This map is in the public domain. Please attribute access and use of this digitized map to the Stephen S. Clark Library, University of Michigan Library.
